{"tid":261357,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"如何在歐洲便宜及平安地旅行","createTime":"2017-05-28T11:39:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-28T12:20:31.000Z","uid":731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"96e66042c0eb231a346fa152fa09f2a8f32242d7","tid":261357,"uid":731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T11:39:37.000Z","msg":"自從2015年11月巴黎恐襲後，好多美國人不敢去歐洲，我多謝他們，因為2016年歐洲郵輪價錢平哂，筆者2016年去了兩次好扺的地中海郵輪。 <br />\n<br />\n當我告訴香港朋友去歐洲時，好多人都說：歐洲好多扒手，你唔怕呀？但有幾個早我退休幾年，成日周圍旅遊的朋友，則說其實歐洲好安全。 <br />\n<br />\n歐洲咁大，面積比中國還大，真的每一吋地方都危險？那麼歐洲的五、六億人如何生活？ <br />\n<br />\n做生意有Risk Management 風險管理去旅行一樣。 <br />\n<br />\n再仔細分析，去歐洲的風險，乃恐襲及扒手。難民問題成日見報，但不會對遊客做成危險。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2sa1SJ5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2sa1SJ5&d=Wx0eNyw6v6BFVWji7AgE%2BYS5T71%2BpEKm9yZKOKwCwR4%3D&h=19c0c116\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2sa1SJ5</a>"},{"pid":"0a65a366b4c1285ff60d09d958fb2c6f0fd65e7c","tid":261357,"uid":89287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T11:42:23.000Z","msg":"其實小心d就唔危險 同睇地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有fd去巴塞幾日比人試過偷三次野<br />\n但我去東北歐十國冇試過 完全冇人想show你"},{"pid":"0ed33586c02ae7a5f868bb88d1a8b500fd8a9329","tid":261357,"uid":17442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T11:45:48.000Z","msg":"六月頭去London 係咪好危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e099ff9c2f4c8dc5c3fa94691883d5e1243dbb52","tid":261357,"uid":76632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T12:16:43.000Z","msg":"google map google earth"},{"pid":"a79f64d0b394c4eedac8722a1b3c1233afd028e8","tid":261357,"uid":47492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T12:20:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>六月頭去London 係咪好危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n生死有命"}]}